== Translate 2024.04 ==
Released at 2024-04-25.

=== Noteworthy changes ===
* Method <code>wfAddNamespace</code> has been deprecated and will be removed in the next MLEB release.
* Implement a minimal prototype for watching message groups. In this early phase, the implementation notifies users about new or deleted messages in the messages groups that they are watching. ({{phab|T348501}})
** Requires the [[Extension:Echo|Echo extension]]
** Requires MW >= 1.41
** Set <code>$wgTranslateEnableMessageGroupSubscription = true;</code> to enable the functionality.
* Show priority language warnings even for discouraged pages ({{phab|T362386}})
* Improve handling of save errors in the Special:Translate interface ({{phab|T360447}})
* Allow enforcing empty priority languages on translatable pages ({{phab|T359975}})
* Allow discouraged groups to be exported ({{phab|T361368}})
* Filter out translation pages from Special:LonelyPages ({{phab|T230456}})
* Use Codex components in Special:PagePreparation ({{phab|T348516}})
* Fix: PageMigration maps translation units incorrectly ({{phab|T344827}})
* Stop translation of message bundle based on prioritylangs and priorityforce ({{phab|T350652}})
* Address contrast issues in night mode ({{phab|T358822}})
* Update import translatable bundle maintenance script to import metadata and automatically mark a page for translation after import. ({{phab|T347155}})
** Read [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/User:APatro_(WMF)/Move_translatable_bundles_across_wiki Move translatable bundles across wiki] for more information on this script.
* Add magic word to embed the translation language outside of translation units ({{phab|T224810}})
* Fix: <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>Enter</kbd> to go to the next message doesnâ€™t work in edit summary field ({{phab|T334354}})
* Add functionality to hide translations to Special:PrefixIndex ({{phab|T299308}})
* Other localisation and maintenance updates.
